Span.Text: Coordinated by ERDF and drawing on the expertise of six distribution system operators (DSO) and some 27 industrial and scientific centres of excellence, universities and technology manufacturers, Grid4EU is the largest smart grid project co-funded by the European Union.  A scalable, largely off-the-shelf, cloud-enabled Microsoft SharePoint infrastructure was the platform of choice.

"As Microsoft Dynamics CRM is fully integrated with other Microsoft products we use, it isn't perceived as a foreign solution and is quite intuitive to work with. I believe this makes a huge difference."
Marcel Kooter, Global Marketing & Customer Director. IST
BP Integrated Supply & Trading (IST) wanted to evolve in line with its customers' demands and to be able to serve them in a consistent manner from any touchpoint.

Offer secure collaboration capabilities with external parties using Microsoft Office 365's productivity suite.  Suppliers, partners and other stakeholders can work together on activities, projects and industry solution challenges.  Role-based security ensures external resources can only access relevant data, that's strictly controlled.

Ensure governing bodies such as OFWAT and OFGEM are provided with published content that's easy to consume.  The Microsoft Dynamics CRM integrated process and data platform ensures complete visibility and availability of relevant information to stakeholders.  Historical data is easily reviewed to ensure compliance and senior teams have a complete dashboard of performance information.

Make information and resources available to customers in an engaging way, that's controlled and secure, using Microsoft SharePoint-based solutions.  A customer portal provides operational efficiencies based on customers being able to self-serve and engage in more productive ways, including integration of tools like Skype for Business.

Extend resource access to customers, 3rd parties and supply chain partners to enable self-service and to help collaborate on maintaining plant technology and the network.  Ensure the organisation is compliant and relevant information is easily available to stake holders and deliver valuable web based self-serve resources to customers, improving operational efficiencies.
